00:49:14,629 --> 00:49:16,810
that you get the feedback you want from your community.

1000
00:49:19,310 --> 00:49:21,671
So lesson here, probably the lesson of lesson

1001
00:49:21,731 --> 00:49:22,431
for our project.

1002
00:49:24,385 --> 00:49:26,005
You can fail, it's fine.

1003
00:49:26,346 --> 00:49:28,586
We did a lot of mistake, it's fine.

