00:49:29,547 --> 00:49:31,948
Acknowledge, learn out of them,

1005
00:49:32,268 --> 00:49:34,049
become better, and then repeat.

1006
00:49:36,770 --> 00:49:40,591
So as a summary, I want to expose what I feel

