00:49:40,711 --> 00:49:44,393
are the big points that made our project successful.

1008
00:49:46,234 --> 00:49:47,734
One, create a remarkable game

1009
00:49:47,754 --> 00:49:49,095
with unique flavors and emotions.

1010
00:49:50,115 --> 00:49:51,936
Two, consistently redefine the game

1011
00:49:51,976 --> 00:49:53,216
with new content and updates.

1012
00:49:54,034 --> 00:49:56,596
Three, work end-in-end with the community,

1013
00:49:56,876 --> 00:49:57,777
give them ownership.

1014
00:49:58,837 --> 00:50:00,659
Four, be available to your players,

1015
00:50:00,839 --> 00:50:02,740
be transparent, honest, and generous.

1016
00:50:03,781 --> 00:50:06,583
Five, be passionate and stay true to your vision.

1017
00:50:08,424 --> 00:50:09,845
And thank you.

